author: andygumbrecht
msg: ServiceLogger was doing a client host name resolution on every socket just for logging (ouch) - Changed to IP and static log level.
SocketConnectionFactory - Ensure a bad or lost connection gets discarded and cleaned up as early as possible.
Push StackTrace logging to debug level - An off the rails client could fill logs in minutes (dos).

author: rhuijben
msg: (svn_opt__arg_canonicalize_url): Allow '\' inside urls on Windows, when
passed as an argument to a tool. This used to be handled when we only
used a single api for urls, paths, fspaths and relpaths.
